HEADWORD: Sachet
<hw>Sa`chet"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., dim. of
<ets>sac</ets>. See <er>Sac</er>.]</ety> <def>A scent bag, or perfume
cushion, to be laid among handkerchiefs, garments, etc., to perfume
them.</def>⟦br⟧
